So if it wasn't you,
just provide us with a sample,

29:37.970 --> 29:39.301
you'll be on your way.

29:39.340 --> 29:40.932
Why should I help you?

29:40.980 --> 29:42.436
If you choose not to cooperate,

29:42.480 --> 29:44.038
we'll just monitor
your whereabouts

29:44.080 --> 29:45.479
until we can force you to.

29:48.080 --> 29:50.139
Lawyer.

29:50.180 --> 29:51.943
Now.

29:54.060 --> 29:57.211
I'll put a team on him
till we get the paperwork.

29:57.260 --> 29:59.455
If we're lucky, we won't
even need a court order.

29:59.490 --> 30:01.196
He's not gonna
give us a DNA sample,

30:01.230 --> 30:03.926
but perhaps he's got one
floating about in the wild.

30:05.330 --> 30:07.366
(knocking)

30:12.410 --> 30:14.401
(sighs) You really are
on your best behavior.

30:16.340 --> 30:19.047
Must have killed you
not to just pick the lock.

30:19.080 --> 30:20.945
Nonsense. I had several more
seconds worth of waItIng In me.

30:20.980 --> 30:21.947
Your mail.

30:21.980 --> 30:23.379
I did pick that lock.

30:23.420 --> 30:26.912
Although I did not steam open
