39:43.740 --> 39:47.039
Our work, what we do...

39:47.080 --> 39:49.048
it's not just a job now.

39:49.080 --> 39:51.446
It's who I am.

39:51.490 --> 39:53.117
I'm a detective.

39:53.150 --> 39:55.710
I'm ready to embrace that.

39:55.760 --> 39:58.524
I live in this
