I understand that now.

40:15.040 --> 40:17.770
I accept it.
I know what it means.

40:17.810 --> 40:20.608
And what does it mean?

40:23.820 --> 40:27.039
It means that it's ridiculous
for me to think

40:27.090 --> 40:30.912
that... I can have
a normal life.

40:30.960 --> 40:34.123
I'm not gonna do that anymore.

40:34.160 --> 40:36.458
Just like I'm not gonna pretend

40:36.500 --> 40:39.492
this isn't the best place
for us to do our work.

40:39.530 --> 40:40.861
You're always welcome
to come here.

40:40.900 --> 40:42.629
You know that.

40:42.670 --> 40:45.059
You don't understand.

40:47.070 --> 40:49.538
I'm saying
that what I need to do

40:49.580 --> 40:52.902
